{
  "texts": [
    "Consequently, the protein content of the product stands at around 40%, while its average dried oil content amounts to 30% (Amrul et al., 2022).",
    "It is possible to process and isolate the oil fraction from the BSFL's protein content.",
    "Protein levels in BSF protein meals can reach over 60% when they have been defatted (Jeon et al., 2011).",
    "Amino acids make up the protein.",
    "In its basic state, the BSFL's amino acid makeup is strikingly close to the protein content of soybean meal."
  ]
}